<h2>1. Perplexity AI — 🏆 Best for Research & Fact-Finding</h2>
<p>Perplexity AI has emerged as the leading AI-powered search engine and research assistant. Unlike traditional search engines that return links, Perplexity delivers comprehensive answers with cited sources, making it invaluable for data gathering and fact-checking. The Pro Search feature enables deep research capabilities with multi-step reasoning, while file upload analysis lets you extract insights from documents, PDFs, and spreadsheets. It's like having a research assistant that finds, synthesizes, and cites information in seconds.</p>

<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "Compare Q1 2026 revenue growth of major cloud providers (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud) with cited sources"</p>
<ul>
<li>Response time: ~3 seconds (Pro Search: ~12 seconds deep research)</li>
<li>Source citation accuracy: 9.5/10 — inline citations with direct links</li>
<li>Answer comprehensiveness: 9/10 — thorough with follow-up suggestions</li>
<li>File analysis: 8.5/10 — handles PDFs, spreadsheets, documents well</li>
</ul>

